<body ><div id="Section 1" class="mktEditable" ><p style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: black; font-size: 18pt;"><img id="__mce_tmp" src="http://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/honeywell3/images/honeywell_emailheader_logo.png" alt="" /></span></strong></p>
<p style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px;"><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Dear Honeywell Customer,<br />&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">In December, we shared with you our plans to transition our Order Management activities from the Redmond, Washington, site to our new partner, Infosys. We are happy to announce that we are on track for the transition.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Just a quick reminder: <br /></span></p>
<ul style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">
<li><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">All Redmond orders, quotes and status activities will be managed by the Infosys CSR team.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">For processing orders, requesting order status, and order expedites and deliveries, you will contact <a href="mailto:orders@honeywell.com">Orders@Honeywell.com</a><br />&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">For quote requests and quote status, you will contact <a href="mailto:quotes@honeywell.com">Quotes@Honeywell.com</a>&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">For all Aircraft on Ground (AOG) issues, please contact the Honeywell AOG Team at 1-800-601-3099 (US/Canada) or 1-602-365-3099 (International), select phone option #4.<br />&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">For Product Support, please email <a href="mailto:aerotechsupport@honeywell.com">AeroTechSupport@Honeywell.com</a> or call 1-855-808-6500 (US/Canada) or 1-602-365-6500 (International).</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Yours Sincerely, &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="color: #000000; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Honeywell Aerospace</span></p></div>
